com.adobe.cq.social.scf.core

Class SocialEvent<T extends SocialEvent.SocialActions>

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
      • com.adobe.cq.social.scf.core.SocialEvent<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type representing the actions supported by the SocialEvent
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CalendarActionsEvent, CommentEvent, FileLibraryEvent, ForumEvent, IdeationEvent, JournalEvent, MessagingSocialEvent, ModerationEvent, PublishEvent, QnaEvent, ReviewEvent, TallyEvent

    public abstract class SocialEvent<T extends SocialEvent.SocialActions>
extends Event
implements java.io.Serializable
    A generic class to define a Social Event and provide the basic framework and data exposed by events triggered by social actions. This class can be subtyped to define specific social events.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
